title: Frank Lloyd Wright Ornament—Dana Butterfly 3D
description:
A choreography of light as air, laser-etched metal, this architectural snowflake honors the design of Frank Lloyd Wright® (American, 1867–1959). Made in the USA of brass with a shiny palladium finish. Inspired by an entry skylight from Wright’s Dana-Thomas House which is located in Springfield, Illinois. 

3 ¾ x 3 ¾ in.
